{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Cx8he9JwHEWcH6CXVoiBZG","type":"tool_result","content":"     1в†’# Story {{epic_num}}.{{story_num}}: {{story_title}}\n     2в†’\n     3в†’Status: ready-for-dev\n     4в†’\n     5в†’<!-- Note: Validation is optional. Run validate-create-story for quality check before dev-story. -->\n     6в†’\n     7в†’## Story\n     8в†’\n     9в†’As a {{role}},\n    10в†’I want {{action}},\n    11в†’so that {{benefit}}.\n    12в†’\n    13в†’## Acceptance Criteria\n    14в†’\n    15в†’1. [Add acceptance criteria from epics/PRD]\n    16в†’\n    17в†’## Tasks / Subtasks\n    18в†’\n    19в†’- [ ] Task 1 (AC: #)\n    20в†’  - [ ] Subtask 1.1\n    21в†’- [ ] Task 2 (AC: #)\n    22в†’  - [ ] Subtask 2.1\n    23в†’\n    24в†’## Dev Notes\n    25в†’\n    26в†’- Relevant architecture patterns and constraints\n    27в†’- Source tree components to touch\n    28в†’- Testing standards summary\n    29в†’\n    30в†’### Project Structure Notes\n    31в†’\n    32в†’- Alignment with unified project structure (paths, modules, naming)\n    33в†’- Detected conflicts or variances (with rationale)\n    34в†’\n    35в†’### References\n    36в†’\n    37в†’- Cite all technical details with source paths and sections, e.g. [Source: docs/<file>.md#Section]\n    38в†’\n    39в†’<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-START:story-verification -->\n    40в†’## Verification Requirements\n    41в†’\n    42в†’- [ ] Showboat proof document created (`docs/exec-plans/active/<story-key>.proof.md`)\n    43в†’- [ ] All acceptance criteria verified with real-world evidence\n    44в†’- [ ] Test coverage meets target (100%)\n    45в†’\n    46в†’## Documentation Requirements\n    47в†’\n    48в†’- [ ] Relevant AGENTS.md files updated (list modules touched)\n    49в†’- [ ] Exec-plan created in `docs/exec-plans/active/<story-key>.md`\n    50в†’\n    51в†’## Testing Requirements\n    52в†’\n    53в†’- [ ] Unit tests written for all new/changed code\n    54в†’- [ ] Integration tests for cross-module interactions\n    55в†’- [ ] Coverage target: 100%\n    56в†’<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-END:story-verification -->\n    57в†’\n    58в†’## Dev Agent Record\n    59в†’\n    60в†’### Agent Model Used\n    61в†’\n    62в†’{{agent_model_name_version}}\n    63в†’\n    64в†’### Debug Log References\n    65в†’\n    66в†’### Completion Notes List\n    67в†’\n    68в†’### File List\n    69в†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01MpYJycPJfk2nBuCCAUW85g","session_id":"51b9d113-d480-4846-9e18-693f5f89566d","uuid":"b7fa60bf-dd58-47ee-84dc-371d2bea918d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T07:08:39.292Z"}
