{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012oT8mxcefxwuNsQyigYjs2","type":"tool_result","content":"    24в†’## Tasks / Subtasks\n    25в†’\n    26в†’- [ ] Task 1: Create `templates/Dockerfile.verify.rust` (AC: #1, #2)\n    27в†’  - [ ] 1.1 Base image: `FROM rust:1.82-slim`\n    28в†’  - [ ] 1.2 System deps: `apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends python3 python3-pip python3-venv pipx curl jq git` + cache cleanup\n    29в†’  - [ ] 1.3 Semgrep: `RUN pipx install semgrep && pipx ensurepath` + `ENV PATH=\"/root/.local/bin:${PATH}\"`\n    30в†’  - [ ] 1.4 Node.js: Install Node.js 20 LTS via NodeSource (needed for showboat npm package)\n    31в†’  - [ ] 1.5 Showboat + Claude Code: `RUN npm install -g showboat @anthropic-ai/claude-code`\n    32в†’  - [ ] 1.6 Rust tools: `RUN cargo install cargo-tarpaulin`\n    33в†’  - [ ] 1.7 OTLP env vars: all 5 env vars matching existing Dockerfile.verify pattern\n    34в†’  - [ ] 1.8 `WORKDIR /workspace`\n    35в†’- [ ] Task 2: Add `'rust'` to `ProjectType` union in `src/modules/verify/types.ts` (AC: #6)\n    36в†’  - [ ] 2.1 Change `type ProjectType = 'nodejs' | 'python' | 'plugin' | 'generic'` to include `| 'rust'`\n    37в†’- [ ] Task 3: Update `detectProjectType()` in `src/modules/verify/env.ts` (AC: #3)\n    38в†’  - [ ] 3.1 Add `if (stack === 'rust') return 'rust';` after the Python check and before the plugin check\n    39в†’- [ ] Task 4: Update `resolveDockerfileTemplate()` in `src/modules/verify/env.ts` (AC: #5)\n    40в†’  - [ ] 4.1 Add `'rust'` variant support: `const filename = variant === 'generic' ? 'Dockerfile.verify.generic' : variant === 'rust' ? 'Dockerfile.verify.rust' : 'Dockerfile.verify';`\n    41в†’- [ ] Task 5: Add `buildRustImage()` function in `src/modules/verify/env.ts` (AC: #4)\n    42в†’  - [ ] 5.1 Create `buildRustImage(projectDir: string): void` following `buildGenericImage` pattern\n    43в†’  - [ ] 5.2 Create temp build context, copy `Cargo.toml`, `Cargo.lock` (if exists), `src/` directory\n    44в†’  - [ ] 5.3 Use `resolveDockerfileTemplate(projectDir, 'rust')` for the Dockerfile\n    45в†’  - [ ] 5.4 Run `docker build -t codeharness-verify .` in build context\n    46в†’  - [ ] 5.5 Clean up temp build context in `finally` block\n    47в†’- [ ] Task 6: Route Rust projects in `buildVerifyImage()` (AC: #4)\n    48в†’  - [ ] 6.1 Add `else if (projectType === 'rust') { buildRustImage(projectDir); }` after the Python branch (L101)\n    49в†’  - [ ] 6.2 Update the generic/plugin hash skip check (L88) to include `'rust'` вЂ” Rust projects have `target/` not `dist/`, so hash check should be skipped for now\n    50в†’- [ ] Task 7: Add tests in `src/modules/verify/__tests__/verify-env.test.ts` (AC: #3, #5, #6, #8)\n    51в†’  - [ ] 7.1 Test: `detectProjectType()` returns `'rust'` when `detectStack()` returns `'rust'`\n    52в†’  - [ ] 7.2 Test: `buildVerifyImage()` uses Rust Dockerfile for Rust projects\n    53в†’  - [ ] 7.3 Test: `resolveDockerfileTemplate()` resolves `Dockerfile.verify.rust` for variant `'rust'`\n    54в†’- [ ] Task 8: Run full test suite вЂ” zero regressions (AC: #8)\n    55в†’\n    56в†’## Dev Notes\n    57в†’\n    58в†’### Critical: showboat is an npm package"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01QhGcCpAcaboC3HghX1odd7","session_id":"51b9d113-d480-4846-9e18-693f5f89566d","uuid":"b5d496c9-ab2d-43cf-929b-45f9cd29dd55","timestamp":"2026-03-23T07:14:31.906Z"}
