{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01G5eARvBTFDLSPpozuhQTn3","type":"tool_result","content":"     1в†’# Senior Developer Review - Validation Checklist\n     2в†’\n     3в†’- [ ] Story file loaded from `{{story_path}}`\n     4в†’- [ ] Story Status verified as reviewable (review)\n     5в†’- [ ] Epic and Story IDs resolved ({{epic_num}}.{{story_num}})\n     6в†’- [ ] Story Context located or warning recorded\n     7в†’- [ ] Epic Tech Spec located or warning recorded\n     8в†’- [ ] Architecture/standards docs loaded (as available)\n     9в†’- [ ] Tech stack detected and documented\n    10в†’- [ ] MCP doc search performed (or web fallback) and references captured\n    11в†’- [ ] Acceptance Criteria cross-checked against implementation\n    12в†’- [ ] File List reviewed and validated for completeness\n    13в†’- [ ] Tests identified and mapped to ACs; gaps noted\n    14в†’- [ ] Code quality review performed on changed files\n    15в†’- [ ] Security review performed on changed files and dependencies\n    16в†’- [ ] Outcome decided (Approve/Changes Requested/Blocked)\n    17в†’- [ ] Review notes appended under \"Senior Developer Review (AI)\"\n    18в†’- [ ] Change Log updated with review entry\n    19в†’- [ ] Status updated according to settings (if enabled)\n    20в†’- [ ] Sprint status synced (if sprint tracking enabled)\n    21в†’- [ ] Story saved successfully\n    22в†’\n    23в†’_Reviewer: {{user_name}} on {{date}}_\n    24в†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Kg9tLGsBN5iJa4HVEh4QKa","session_id":"51b9d113-d480-4846-9e18-693f5f89566d","uuid":"b1f384e9-779b-4b9d-bcf4-365a0a2a70fe","timestamp":"2026-03-23T07:16:06.371Z"}
