{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Mx1FmhAsRDEQC4Eimmx5BK","type":"tool_result","content":"     1в†’# src/modules/verify -- Story Verification Module\n     2в†’\n     3в†’Handles story verification, proof document parsing, black-box verifier agent orchestration,\n     4в†’and Docker environment management for isolated verification.\n     5в†’\n     6в†’## Module Structure\n     7в†’\n     8в†’| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n     9в†’|------|---------|-------------|\n    10в†’| index.ts | Public interface вЂ” delegates to internal files | `verifyStory`, `parseProof`, re-exports all public types/functions |\n    11в†’| orchestrator.ts | Verification pipeline orchestration | `checkPreconditions`, `createProofDocument`, `runShowboatVerify`, `updateVerificationState`, `closeBeadsIssue` |\n    12в†’| parser.ts | Story AC extraction and classification | `parseStoryACs`, `classifyAC`, `classifyVerifiability`, `classifyStrategy`, `parseVerificationTag` |\n    13в†’| proof.ts | Proof quality validation + black-box enforcement | `validateProofQuality`, `proofHasContent`, `classifyEvidenceCommands`, `checkBlackBoxEnforcement` |\n    14в†’| env.ts | Docker image lifecycle + clean workspace + stale container cleanup | `buildVerifyImage`, `prepareVerifyWorkspace`, `checkVerifyEnv`, `cleanupVerifyEnv`, `cleanupStaleContainers`, `isValidStoryKey`, `computeDistHash` |\n    15в†’| browser.ts | Agent-browser integration for UI testing in Docker | `BrowserVerifier` class with `navigate`, `screenshot`, `click`, `type`, `evaluate`, `isAvailable`, `diffScreenshots` |\n    16в†’| types.ts | All verify domain types | `VerifyResult`, `ProofQuality`, `ParsedAC`, `BuildOptions`, `BuildResult`, `CheckResult`, `BrowserActionResult`, `DiffResult`, etc. |\n    17в†’| validation-acs.ts | Validation AC registry barrel вЂ” combines all 79 ACs | `VALIDATION_ACS`, `getACsByCategory`, `getCliVerifiableACs`, `getIntegrationRequiredACs`, `getACById` |\n    18в†’| validation-ac-types.ts | Types for validation AC entries | `ValidationAC`, `VerificationMethod`, `AcCategory` |\n    19в†’| validation-ac-fr.ts | FR validation AC data (ACs 1-40) | `FR_ACS` |\n    20в†’| validation-ac-data.ts | NFR/UX/Regression/ActionItem AC data (ACs 41-79) | `NFR_ACS`, `UX_ACS`, `REGRESSION_ACS`, `ACTION_ITEM_ACS` |\n    21в†’| validation-runner.ts | Validation infrastructure: sprint init, AC execution, fix story gen, result processing | `createValidationSprint`, `executeValidationAC`, `createFixStory`, `processValidationResult` |\n    22в†’| validation-orchestrator.ts | Validation orchestration: cycle execution, progress tracking | `runValidationCycle`, `getValidationProgress` |\n    23в†’| validation-runner-types.ts | Types for validation runner | `ValidationACResult`, `ValidationSprintResult`, `ValidationCycleResult`, `ValidationProgress`, `ValidationVerdict` |\n    24в†’\n    25в†’## Module Boundary\n    26в†’\n    27в†’Only `index.ts` should be imported from outside this module. Internal files (`orchestrator.ts`, `parser.ts`, `proof.ts`, `env.ts`) are not part of the public API.\n    28в†’\n    29в†’## Tests (`__tests__/`)\n    30в†’\n    31в†’| File | Tests For | Source Location |\n    32в†’|------|-----------|-----------------|\n    33в†’| index.test.ts | Module delegation (verifyStory, parseProof) | `./index.ts` |\n    34в†’| verify.test.ts | Orchestrator + proof quality validation | `./orchestrator.ts`, `./proof.ts` |\n    35в†’| verify-blackbox.test.ts | Black-box enforcement logic | `./proof.ts` |\n    36в†’| verify-prompt.test.ts | Verifier prompt generation | `src/templates/verify-prompt.ts` |\n    37в†’| verify-env.test.ts | Environment checks (Docker, workspace) | `./env.ts` |\n    38в†’| verify-parser.test.ts | Story AC parsing, classification | `./parser.ts` |\n    39в†’| verifier-session.test.ts | Verifier session management | `src/lib/verifier-session.ts` |\n    40в†’| browser.test.ts | BrowserVerifier unit tests (mocked docker exec) | `./browser.ts` |\n    41в†’| validation-acs.test.ts | Validation AC registry: count, structure, distribution, helpers | `./validation-acs.ts` |\n    42в†’| validation-runner.test.ts | Validation runner: sprint init, AC execution, fix stories, result processing, orchestration | `./validation-runner.ts`, `./validation-orchestrator.ts` |\n    43в†’| verification-observability-patch.test.ts | Patch content validation + observability integration regression tests | `patches/verify/story-verification.md`, `src/templates/verify-prompt.ts`, `./parser.ts` |\n    44в†’\n    45в†’## Architecture Notes\n    46в†’\n    47в†’- All public functions return `Result<T>` (via `verifyStory`, `parseProof`) or throw (legacy direct exports).\n    48в†’- Old `src/lib/verify.ts`, `src/lib/verify-parser.ts`, `src/lib/verify-env.ts` have been deleted.\n    49в†’- Commands (`src/commands/verify.ts`, `src/commands/verify-env.ts`, `src/commands/validate.ts`) import only from `./index.ts`.\n    50в†’- The `codeharness status` command imports `getValidationProgress` from `./index.ts` for real-time validation display.\n    51в†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Kg9tLGsBN5iJa4HVEh4QKa","session_id":"51b9d113-d480-4846-9e18-693f5f89566d","uuid":"f3ea22a1-9eb0-4d1f-841c-4754c7a414b1","timestamp":"2026-03-23T07:16:30.789Z"}
