{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018G6dJjGajwpF5UnisuJ88J","type":"tool_result","content":"   205в†’<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-END:story-verification -->\n   206в†’\n   207в†’## Dev Agent Record\n   208в†’\n   209в†’### Agent Model Used\n   210в†’\n   211в†’Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context)\n   212в†’\n   213в†’### Debug Log References\n   214в†’\n   215в†’### Completion Notes List\n   216в†’\n   217в†’- Created `templates/Dockerfile.verify.rust` with rust:1.82-slim base, Python+Semgrep via pipx, Node.js 20 via NodeSource, showboat+claude-code via npm, cargo-tarpaulin, all 5 OTLP env vars, WORKDIR /workspace\n   218в†’- Added `'rust'` to `ProjectType` union in types.ts\n   219в†’- Added Rust detection in `detectProjectType()` вЂ” returns `'rust'` when `detectStack()` returns `'rust'`\n   220в†’- Updated `resolveDockerfileTemplate()` to resolve `Dockerfile.verify.rust` for variant `'rust'`\n   221в†’- Added `buildRustImage()` function following `buildGenericImage` pattern (Dockerfile-only build context, 300s timeout for cargo install)\n   222в†’- Routed Rust projects in `buildVerifyImage()` and added `'rust'` to the hash-skip list (no dist/ for Rust)\n   223в†’- Updated existing test that expected `'rust'` в†’ `'generic'` to expect `'rust'` в†’ `'rust'`\n   224в†’- Added 3 new tests: Rust image build, no dist/ requirement, Dockerfile template resolution\n   225в†’- Full suite: 2998 tests pass, zero regressions\n   226в†’\n   227в†’### File List\n   228в†’\n   229в†’- `templates/Dockerfile.verify.rust` (new)\n   230в†’- `src/modules/verify/types.ts` (modified)\n   231в†’- `src/modules/verify/env.ts` (modified)\n   232в†’- `src/modules/verify/__tests__/verify-env.test.ts` (modified)\n   233в†’- `_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/8-6-rust-verification-dockerfile.md` (modified)\n   234в†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"51b9d113-d480-4846-9e18-693f5f89566d","uuid":"8cc70b3d-78aa-413f-b15e-0d20b5692fee","timestamp":"2026-03-23T07:24:59.000Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/8-6-rust-verification-dockerfile.md","content":"<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-END:story-verification -->\n\n## Dev Agent Record\n\n### Agent Model Used\n\nClaude Opus 4.6 (1M context)\n\n### Debug Log References\n\n### Completion Notes List\n\n- Created `templates/Dockerfile.verify.rust` with rust:1.82-slim base, Python+Semgrep via pipx, Node.js 20 via NodeSource, showboat+claude-code via npm, cargo-tarpaulin, all 5 OTLP env vars, WORKDIR /workspace\n- Added `'rust'` to `ProjectType` union in types.ts\n- Added Rust detection in `detectProjectType()` вЂ” returns `'rust'` when `detectStack()` returns `'rust'`\n- Updated `resolveDockerfileTemplate()` to resolve `Dockerfile.verify.rust` for variant `'rust'`\n- Added `buildRustImage()` function following `buildGenericImage` pattern (Dockerfile-only build context, 300s timeout for cargo install)\n- Routed Rust projects in `buildVerifyImage()` and added `'rust'` to the hash-skip list (no dist/ for Rust)\n- Updated existing test that expected `'rust'` в†’ `'generic'` to expect `'rust'` в†’ `'rust'`\n- Added 3 new tests: Rust image build, no dist/ requirement, Dockerfile template resolution\n- Full suite: 2998 tests pass, zero regressions\n\n### File List\n\n- `templates/Dockerfile.verify.rust` (new)\n- `src/modules/verify/types.ts` (modified)\n- `src/modules/verify/env.ts` (modified)\n- `src/modules/verify/__tests__/verify-env.test.ts` (modified)\n- `_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/8-6-rust-verification-dockerfile.md` (modified)\n","numLines":30,"startLine":205,"totalLines":234}}}
