tion\": \"**AC4 verified via function replication, not CLI.** `parseTestCounts` is internal and not exercised by any CLI subcommand that accepts raw test output. No `codeharness parse-test-output` command.\",\n   413в†’      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   414в†’      \"resolved\": false\n   415в†’    },\n   416в†’    {\n   417в†’      \"id\": \"migrated-18\",\n   418в†’      \"story\": \"8-3-cargo-tarpaulin-coverage-detection\",\n   419в†’      \"description\": \"**[OBSERVABILITY GAP]** No log entries in VictoriaLogs during verification. Expected вЂ” container doesn't have Docker-in-Docker so observability stack not running inside it.\",\n   420в†’      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   421в†’      \"resolved\": false\n   422в†’    },\n   423в†’    {\n   424в†’      \"id\": \"migrated-19\",\n   425в†’      \"story\": \"8-3-cargo-tarpaulin-coverage-detection\",\n   426в†’      \"description\": \"**Workspace aggregation confirmed.** Bundle shows `parseTestCounts` uses global regex with `matchAll`-style loop for multi-crate workspace test output.\",\n   427в†’      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   428в†’      \"resolved\": false\n   429в†’    },\n   430в†’    {\n   431в†’      \"id\": \"migrated-20\",\n   432в†’      \"story\": \"8-4-register-cargo-tarpaulin-dep-registry\",\n   433в†’      \"description\": \"**Unconditional dependency registry:** Adding `cargo-tarpaulin` means `cargo install cargo-tarpaulin` will be attempted on all projects regardless of stack. Fails gracefully (`critical: false`) but is noisy. Stack-conditional filtering would be a separate story.\",\n   434в†’      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   435в†’      \"resolved\": false\n   436в†’    },\n   437в†’    {\n   438в†’      \"id\": \"migrated-21\",\n   439в†’      \"story\": \"8-4-register-cargo-tarpaulin-dep-registry\",\n   440в†’      \"description\": \"**Pre-existing stub overwritten:** The file already existed as a skeleton from sprint planning. Overwritten with comprehensive story as expected.\",\n   441в†’      \